Firstly, we are inserting the string characters in stack if they are open brackets like ( "[" , "(" , "[" ), then if they're other than open bracket, then we are comparing the stack top element if it is a pair of the string character or not, while makink sure that our stack is non empty.
If we find a **valid pair with string character** then we are popping that character from the stack.
At the end, if our stack comes out to be empty then return true, else return false.

