This solution uses functionality like stack to solve the problem . As stack is LIFO structure so if for each open parenthesis such as ( OR { OR [ we have to insert corresponding closing parenthesis ) OR } OR ] .

So each time we iterate and get an open parenthesis we push the closing parenthesis and if we encounter a closing parenthesis we check and pop depending on the comparison .We can first ignore the ones which are of off length . At the enf of the program we have to check if the stack is empty or not . if not it's false . Vice versa .

